text: Clairton Norchang Netto (born 28 February 1998) is a Brazilian professional footballer who plays as a forward for Mirassol. ==Professional career== A youth product of São Paulo FC, Netto was released in 2018 after a knee surgery, and signed with Internacional. Netto made his professional debut with Internacional in a 4-3 Campeonato Gaúcho win over São Luiz on 30 January 2020. ==References== ==External links== * * Internacional Profile Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Minas Gerais Category:Brazilian footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:Sport Club Internacional players Category:Campeonato Brasileiro Série A players
